  ::text
    On level up, they receive 2 skill points that they may allocate as they choose.

    Skills cap at 5.

    0 points in something usually indicates you cannot do that thing at
    all (completely untrained), with the exception of things like
    climbing.

    Skill checks are either gated (you need X in skill to do Y) or are a d6+skill roll against a target number.

